# Final Report

**Unit:** ADS2001 – Data Challenges  
**Year:** 2025

## Overview

This folder contains the final project report developed for ADS2001.

The report documents the complete data science workflow, including problem definition, data preparation, exploratory analysis, model development, evaluation, and recommendations.

## Purpose

The report was developed as a stakeholder-facing document to communicate:

- The project background and objectives
- Data quality assessment and preparation methods
- Exploratory data analysis findings
- Modelling approaches and evaluation results
- Conclusions and recommendations based on the analysis

The report focuses on translating technical analysis into actionable insights and data-driven recommendations.
